	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "10"
	"message" "Downloaded it, launched it... 'Well... I'll see what it's all about,' you said.\nFor one evening. And here you are, at the very end. But tell me honestly..."
	"targetname" "narrator_monologue4"
