	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "255 228 0"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "10"
	"message" "Two hundred. Fucking two hundred people.\n\nAnd do you know how many comments there are? Almost none. Zero. The developer wrote articles. Long articles."
	"targetname" "narrator_monologue6"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "-248 -168 8"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[0 6500]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "166"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "255 228 0"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "10"
	"message" "Calling them, rather nicely,\n'Manifestos.' Wrote about new versions, what he'd added. More about plans, future plots... Made an ARG... Updated the game."
	"targetname" "narrator_monologue7"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "-248 -152 8"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[0 6500]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "173"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "255 228 0"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "10"
	"message" "Over and over again. Tell me, for what purpose? For those worthless two hundred downloads?\n\nFor the peace and quiet? And don't close the game now, player. I know you want to, but I haven't finished yet."
	"targetname" "narrator_monologue8"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "-232 -248 8"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[0 6500]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "180"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "0"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "255 228 0"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "10"
	"message" "Answer the question. Oh, right. You can't. /n Okay. I'll give you a button."
	"targetname" "narrator_monologue9"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "-216 -248 8"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[0 6500]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "225"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "255 228 0"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "10"
	"message" "The player said nothing. He couldn't say anything.\nEven if he wanted to. The narrator continued talking.\nAs always. He wrote long manifestos."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "writer_dialogue"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "-24 -8 8"
