	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "10"
	"message" "But simply because... his motivation isn't even clear. He blindly hopes that someone will notice him.\nBut he continues to speak to nothing. It's quite charming to watch him."
